2. **Sensitivity analysis:** Plot portfolio Sharpe ratio as a function of: (a) number of assets in universe, (b) rebalancing frequency (daily/weekly/monthly), (c) covariance estimation window (63, 126, 252 days). Use `matplotlib` subplots.
